  <section class="section launch-purpose">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <p class="launch-kicker">Why we are organising now</p>
      <h2>A direct route to an outcome owners can support</h2>
      <div class="stack">
        <p class="launch-lead">
          Individual owners have different experiences and different priorities. An organised
          group can gather those views responsibly, show where owners agree, and give JLR a
          practical way to respond to the people affected.
        </p>
        <p>
          Data-protection rules rightly prevent JLR from simply sharing customer details so
          owners can find one another. This independent, consent-based group gives owners a
          safe way to come together and speak with collective weight.
        </p>
        <div class="callout callout--info">
          <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
          <div class="callout__content">
            <p class="callout__title">This is an advocacy group, not another forum</p>
            <p>Our purpose is to understand what owners need, represent those views clearly,
            and pursue a fair and consistent resolution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid--2 launch-route-grid">
        <article class="card card--accent">
          <p class="launch-kicker">Our preferred route</p>
          <h2 class="card__title">A constructive agreement</h2>
          <div class="card__body">
            <p>We want to help JLR understand the range of owner preferences and reach a
            broadly acceptable solution before Jaguar's next vehicle launch. A prompt,
            positive outcome would benefit owners, JLR, and confidence in the brand.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <p class="launch-kicker">If that route fails</p>
          <h2 class="card__title">Owners keep their options</h2>
          <div class="card__body">
            <p>An organised group is prepared to consider other appropriate routes if
            constructive engagement does not succeed. Joining now does not enrol you in
            legal action. Any future proposal would be explained separately, and each owner
            would choose whether to take part.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section launch-final-cta">
    <div class="container container--narrow text-center">
      <h2>Add your voice</h2>
      <p>Membership helps us show that I-PACE owners are organised and ready to engage.
      You only need your name and email address to join.</p>
      <a href="/join/" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Join the Group</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

